Package: cad-preprocess
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.9), python3-pip, ${misc:Depends}
Description: DICOM preprocessing tool for CAD systems
 CAD Preprocess is a reusable preprocessing software for medical
 DICOM images to support CAD (Computer-Aided Detection/Diagnosis)
 systems. It standardizes preprocessing across training, inference,
 and UI workflows.
 .
 Features:
  - DICOM file discovery and validation
  - Deterministic image preprocessing pipeline
  - Profile-based metadata extraction
  - Configurable output formats
  - CLI and Python API interfaces
